00:17:14,925 --> 00:17:17,405
and it didn't even reach 100,000 yuan.

262
00:17:17,565 --> 00:17:20,045
I'm due to pay him by tomorrow the latest.

263
00:17:20,244 --> 00:17:22,364
And I haven't even
joined the Student Council.

264
00:17:22,925 --> 00:17:26,525
Am I going to be kicked out of college
just because I don't have the money?

265
00:17:30,364 --> 00:17:32,445
DANIEL, CELEBRITY BROKER

266
00:17:34,125 --> 00:17:36,965
Mr. Zhou, I've paid up
all the compensation.

267
00:17:37,045 --> 00:17:40,125
-Don't break the rules next time.
-Yes, sir.

268
00:17:40,205 --> 00:17:42,285
I'll follow what you told me.

269
00:17:42,405 --> 00:17:43,725
May I go back to class now?

270
00:17:45,085 --> 00:17:46,005
See you, sir.

271
00:17:48,325 --> 00:17:50,685
-What are you doing here?
-Mind your own business.

272
00:17:52,565 --> 00:17:53,485
Hey.

273
00:17:54,325 --> 00:17:57,245
I heard you're now Feng's assistant.

274
00:17:58,725 --> 00:17:59,765
Boy, the word got out fast.

275
00:18:00,445 --> 00:18:03,165
That's right, I'm Feng's new assistant.

276
00:18:03,245 --> 00:18:06,205
I'm his private, personal assistant.

277
00:18:07,005 --> 00:18:09,925
Stop putting up an act.
I know that already.

278
00:18:10,765 --> 00:18:13,485
But you're only an assistant by name.

279
00:18:14,565 --> 00:18:16,525
That's what others think.

280
00:18:16,605 --> 00:18:19,125
Now, I'm not only Situ Feng's deskmate.

281
00:18:19,765 --> 00:18:20,925
I'm now his assistant.

282
00:18:21,685 --> 00:18:24,725
His private, personal assistant.

283
00:18:25,005 --> 00:18:26,045
And you.

284
00:18:26,525 --> 00:18:28,645
You're none of that.

285
00:18:34,925 --> 00:18:37,365
Did Qingqing really agree
to be your assistant?

286
00:18:38,445 --> 00:18:39,565
That crazy bitch.

287
00:18:39,645 --> 00:18:43,165
She said she wasn't a fan of mine,
yet she bought a lot of tickets.

288
00:18:43,885 --> 00:18:45,565
I think you should be more careful.

289
00:18:45,885 --> 00:18:49,445
You once said, whoever crosses you,
it's not going to end well for them.

290
00:18:50,005 --> 00:18:52,205
I see that things haven't been great
for you lately.

291
00:18:56,965 --> 00:18:59,125
This is the last one.

292
00:18:59,205 --> 00:19:01,205
Thanks for coming.

293
00:19:01,725 --> 00:19:03,445
-Bye.
-Bye.

294
00:19:06,765 --> 00:19:07,605
Chen Qingqing.

295
00:19:08,085 --> 00:19:09,205
What are you doing?

296
00:19:09,285 --> 00:19:12,525
I didn't think your tickets
would sell so well.

297
00:19:12,605 --> 00:19:15,925
All I did was post it
on the college's discussion forum

298
00:19:16,005 --> 00:19:17,725
and everyone started asking
about the cost.

299
00:19:17,805 --> 00:19:19,765
So I earned a lot
by reselling the tickets.

300
00:19:19,845 --> 00:19:21,365
-Qingqing, you--
-Hey.

301
00:19:24,285 --> 00:19:26,325
You didn't like her errands service,
right?

302
00:19:26,405 --> 00:19:28,685
She'll stop the service
after she gets the money she needs.

303
00:19:28,925 --> 00:19:30,885
Just like what you wanted.

304
00:19:31,565 --> 00:19:33,125
What did you say about me?

305
00:19:34,005 --> 00:19:35,005
Nothing.

306
00:19:37,445 --> 00:19:39,205
QINGQING'S ERRANDS SERVICE
OPEN FOR BUSINESS

307
00:19:52,125 --> 00:19:54,725
Come on!

308
00:19:54,965 --> 00:19:59,365
Golden VIP seats up for rent!

309
00:20:00,005 --> 00:20:01,325
Right next to His Highness!

310
00:20:01,405 --> 00:20:03,165
Nothing is stopping you to be with him.

311
00:20:03,245 --> 00:20:06,445
Sometimes you may
run into him by accident.

312
00:20:06,525 --> 00:20:09,565
It's a real face-to-face contact!

313
00:20:09,805 --> 00:20:12,645
Limited seats available.
Hurry while stocks last!

314
00:20:13,205 --> 00:20:14,285
SEAT FOR RENT - HIS HIGHNESS

315
00:20:14,525 --> 00:20:17,205
Qingqing, don't you have
enough money already?

316
00:20:17,765 --> 00:20:19,605
Even so, I can still earn more, right?

317
00:20:20,365 --> 00:20:22,165
Besides, I've thought about it.

318
00:20:22,245 --> 00:20:25,405
Neither of us want to share the same desk
with each other.

319
00:20:25,485 --> 00:20:28,605
So instead, why don't I rent out my seat?

320
00:20:28,845 --> 00:20:34,005
It just happens that I can help
those pure-hearted girls that like you.

321
00:20:35,805 --> 00:20:37,925
Hey! What the hell, Situ Feng?

322
00:20:38,005 --> 00:20:41,485
Your errands service
should stop right now!

323
00:20:43,045 --> 00:20:43,925
You can go now.

324
00:20:44,525 --> 00:20:46,325
Hey, don't go!

325
00:20:47,805 --> 00:20:49,685
Situ Feng, why are you doing this?

326
00:20:50,445 --> 00:20:52,005
Because you're my assistant.

327
00:20:52,645 --> 00:20:57,445
Once you signed up to be my assistant,
if you breach the contract,

328
00:20:57,965 --> 00:21:01,725
you'll need to compensate me more
than that painting is going to cost you.

329
00:21:03,765 --> 00:21:04,685
Fine.

330
00:21:04,765 --> 00:21:07,485
I am your assistant, Situ Feng.

331
00:21:07,565 --> 00:21:10,725
Chen Qingqing is a woman of her word.

332
00:21:11,285 --> 00:21:13,965
All right, my assistant.
Get me some water.

333
00:21:16,645 --> 00:21:17,485
Go!

334
00:21:22,965 --> 00:21:24,365
Hey, you spilled the water!

335
00:21:24,445 --> 00:21:25,725
Aren't you going to drink it?

336
00:21:28,245 --> 00:21:31,725
Hey, cold water? How many times do I have
to tell you? I have a sensitive stomach!

337
00:21:39,565 --> 00:21:41,085
Hey, the water is so hot!

338
00:21:41,165 --> 00:21:43,125
Do you want me to burn my tongue?
Get another one.

339
00:21:55,485 --> 00:21:59,885
Your gym teacher has an emergency.
We'll have math instead.

340
00:22:00,445 --> 00:22:02,045
Distribute the papers.

341
00:22:07,805 --> 00:22:09,685
Let's see how badly you did.

342
00:22:10,245 --> 00:22:11,685
Situ Feng.

343
00:22:12,765 --> 00:22:14,525
I'm warning you.

344
00:22:15,085 --> 00:22:18,325
You'd better not leave anything
I can use against you.

345
00:22:18,685 --> 00:22:20,645
If not...

346
00:22:25,205 --> 00:22:26,445
Situ Feng.

347
00:22:27,005 --> 00:22:29,205
Do you know that you scored
the lowest in your class?

348
00:22:29,365 --> 00:22:31,965
And you've lowered the class average
by three points.

349
00:22:32,445 --> 00:22:34,365
When I call your names,

350
00:22:34,845 --> 00:22:37,565
you'll be paired up into study groups.

351
00:22:37,645 --> 00:22:38,845
Group One.

352
00:22:39,805 --> 00:22:42,005
Chen Qingqing, Situ Feng.

353
00:22:43,245 --> 00:22:44,085
Group Two.

354
00:22:44,725 --> 00:22:47,525
Ms. Chen, I don't want to be with her!

355
00:22:48,525 --> 00:22:49,725
Ms. Chen.

356
00:22:50,485 --> 00:22:52,805
I am very happy to accept
your arrangement.

357
00:22:53,485 --> 00:22:54,965
As part of this class,

358
00:22:55,045 --> 00:22:57,565
I am willing to help

359
00:22:57,645 --> 00:22:58,925
someone physically underdeveloped

360
00:22:59,005 --> 00:23:00,845
and simple-minded students

361
00:23:00,925 --> 00:23:03,325
to step up with me
and defend the class' honor.

362
00:23:03,405 --> 00:23:04,325
That's good.

363
00:23:04,965 --> 00:23:06,965
Situ Feng, do you have any objections?

364
00:23:09,885 --> 00:23:11,165
No, ma'am.

365
00:23:12,325 --> 00:23:14,525
We're going to have a welcoming party
this weekend.

366
00:23:15,125 --> 00:23:17,405
Every class has to come out
with a program.

367
00:23:17,485 --> 00:23:19,045
Do you have any ideas?

368
00:23:19,325 --> 00:23:20,565
Situ Feng should sing!

369
00:23:20,645 --> 00:23:22,685
-Sing!
-Sing!

370
00:23:22,765 --> 00:23:24,885
This requires the approval
of those involved.

371
00:23:25,365 --> 00:23:28,165
Situ Feng, do you have any objections?

372
00:23:28,685 --> 00:23:29,525
No.

373
00:23:32,925 --> 00:23:33,765
Keep quiet now.

374
00:23:33,845 --> 00:23:35,365
Let's discuss the papers.

375
00:23:35,445 --> 00:23:37,165
Please refer to your papers.

376
00:23:37,245 --> 00:23:39,725
First, let's look at question two.

377
00:24:14,325 --> 00:24:17,245
You were so pleased with yourself,
weren't you, Situ Feng?

378
00:24:17,325 --> 00:24:22,085
Now, let me show you what you get
when you cross Chen Qingqing.

379
00:24:27,805 --> 00:24:28,845
Miss Chen Qingqing.

380
00:24:28,925 --> 00:24:31,645
-We're so sorry for what we did.
-Yeah.

381
00:24:31,725 --> 00:24:33,005
We didn't acknowledge you.

382
00:24:33,085 --> 00:24:37,045
-We didn't acknowledge you.
-Yes, if you could just forgive us.

383
00:24:37,325 --> 00:24:39,965
-We'll do anything to make it up to you.
-That's right.

384
00:24:40,045 --> 00:24:42,725
You just have to share with us
His Highness's latest news!

385
00:24:42,805 --> 00:24:44,765
Or you can just recommend us to him.

386
00:24:45,765 --> 00:24:49,085
We're so envious that you can be
by His Highness's side every day!

387
00:24:49,365 --> 00:24:53,885
That skin, those lips, that slender--

388
00:24:54,125 --> 00:24:55,445
Okay, stop it.

389
00:24:56,845 --> 00:24:59,125
I've told you before, right?

390
00:25:00,125 --> 00:25:01,405
The reason why

391
00:25:01,485 --> 00:25:04,565
they took pictures of me
with Situ Feng like that

392
00:25:04,645 --> 00:25:10,845
was because we seem to be
good friends in private.

393
00:25:10,925 --> 00:25:14,645
They didn't even care what sexes we are!

394
00:25:16,525 --> 00:25:17,725
Besides,

395
00:25:18,125 --> 00:25:19,845
for someone like Situ Feng...

396
00:25:20,325 --> 00:25:23,605
He's usually quite unmanly, you know?

397
00:25:28,005 --> 00:25:29,285
Lucky for you.

398
00:25:29,365 --> 00:25:32,085
Everyone is getting ready
for the welcoming party.

399
00:25:32,405 --> 00:25:33,805
We could use more hands here.

400
00:25:34,565 --> 00:25:36,365
So I've told the secretariat about it

401
00:25:36,965 --> 00:25:38,445
and they're willing to take you in.

402
00:25:38,925 --> 00:25:40,245
I'll surely get the job done!

403
00:25:43,245 --> 00:25:44,605
By the way, Mr. Gu.

404
00:25:44,685 --> 00:25:46,045
Can I ask you something?

405
00:25:46,125 --> 00:25:48,685
Which department is in charge

406
00:25:49,005 --> 00:25:50,605
of our college archives?

407
00:25:51,605 --> 00:25:54,565
Ming De's college archives are top secret.

408
00:25:54,645 --> 00:25:56,885
Only those in the presidium
can access them.

409
00:25:57,565 --> 00:25:59,445
Qingqing, why did you ask?

410
00:26:00,165 --> 00:26:03,285
Oh, it's nothing. I'm just curious.

411
00:26:04,005 --> 00:26:06,925
You've had a little misunderstanding
with someone in the council.

412
00:26:07,005 --> 00:26:08,645
You're just in time to clear the air.

413
00:26:09,765 --> 00:26:10,605
Come on.

414
00:26:17,805 --> 00:26:18,685
Chen Qingqing...

415
00:26:24,285 --> 00:26:25,245
Chen Qingqing...

416
00:26:34,885 --> 00:26:37,605
Chen Qingqing, you're right on time.

417
00:26:38,885 --> 00:26:40,525
It's you again?

418
00:26:55,365 --> 00:26:56,365
I hope you don't mind.

419
00:26:56,445 --> 00:26:59,045
I don't blame you, but personal hygiene
is my highest priority.

420
00:27:00,445 --> 00:27:02,485
Aren't we studying math?
What are we doing here?

421
00:27:02,565 --> 00:27:05,605
It's so peaceful and quiet here,
so it's the best place to study.

422
00:27:07,485 --> 00:27:10,405
I wrote this song for her.

423
00:27:13,845 --> 00:27:15,165
What the hell happened?

424
00:27:15,285 --> 00:27:16,205
Who's there?

425
00:27:16,285 --> 00:27:18,045
Is something wrong with me?

426
00:27:18,125 --> 00:27:20,365
It's 120 beats per minute?

427
00:27:20,925 --> 00:27:22,925
Isn't there anyone you like?

428
00:27:23,005 --> 00:27:25,645
I'm Chen Qingqing. Who would I like?

429
00:27:28,045 --> 00:27:29,925
Subtitle translation by CL Tan
